[[/SECTION]]

[[SECTION]]
TITLE: Software Component Design Specification

[TEXT]
STATEMENT: >>>
This section constitutes the Software Component Design Specification as
required by EN 50716:2023, Clause 7.4 and Table A.1 (document 15). The
specification provides the detailed design of each software component,
including its interface contract, internal logic, state behaviour, and
data structures, at the level of granularity required for implementation
and independent verification.

One complete set of sub-sections 2.1 through 2.3 shall be produced for
each software component listed in the architecture (SAD-011). The component
identifier <COMP-ID> shall be replaced with the actual module identifier
throughout each set.
<<<

